\approx \frac{386}{6.022}\times 10^{-23}\ \text{g}
\approx 64.1\times 10^{-23}\ \text{g}
=6.41\times 10^{-22}\ \text{g}
\]

So the correct choice is **(A) 6.41 × 10^-22 g**.

